init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Each of them will be a specialist on one aspect of the operation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These agents will need to battle space pirates, smugglers, and of course the alien emperor.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The rocketship took off to space and blasted toward their destination.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien spacecraft was not too far away, but as the crew got closer they noticed something odd.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The UN task force needed to act fast.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The space shuttle went for the alien spacecraft and pursued it to prevent any other space pirates from taking Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The UN space shuttle was not going to accept this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They even offered a better actor, Will Smith.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He told the agents that they will hold out for Nicholas Cage, but if he does not come with them then Matt Damon would never see Earth again.
